description.en: Launched on December 31, 2018 in Brazil, NFXCoin is the native token of NFXTRADER, a new exchange that aims to present new features with the integration of dozens of cryptocurrencies in its portfolio and launch a new concept of the relationship of its users with money . Any user of the platform, choosing to pay transaction fees with our native token, will pay only 50% of the trading fees provided by the platform. The entire basis of the NFX Project is based on a concept of facilitation, innovation, convenience, security and efficiency in transactions involving values. The financial center of the NFX Project will be NFXPay, where through a friendly platform and with a high level of security, users will be able to transact values ​​instantly and at an extremely low cost. Finally, bonus programs and cashbacks will be present on each new platform launched by the NFX Project, making its use grateful for its users.
